How Is Your Information Collected?:\u003c/div\u003e\",\"info_text\":[{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe collect information that you enter on our digital properties or give to us in other ways (e.g., when you contact Guest Relations, order on Target.com, purchase a product in a Target store or create a gift registry).\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"YouProvide\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eYou Provide It to Us\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may connect information collected automatically with information we already have about you in order to identify you as a Target Guest. If we are able to identify you as a Target Guest we may, for example, link your activity on our website to your activity in a Target store or on one of our mobile application(s). This allows us to provide you with a personalized experience regardless of how you interact with us \u0026#8211; online, in store, mobile, etc.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIn order to provide the best Guest experience possible and run our business operations, we also use automated information collection technologies for reporting and analysis purposes. We examine metrics such as how you are shopping on our website, in our stores, and on our mobile application(s), the performance of our marketing efforts, and your response to those marketing efforts.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"Third\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cb\u003eThird-party Automated Collection\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe and our service providers use anonymous identifiers such as cookies and other technologies to collect and store certain types of information (e.g., click stream information, browser type, time and date, subject of advertisements clicked or scrolled over, hardware/software information, cookie and session ID) whenever you interact with us or third-parties that use our services.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe also allow third-party companies (e.g., Google) to place tags on our digital properties once approved through our tagging process. The tags may collect information from your interactions on Target.com. Our Privacy Policy does not cover these third party companies. Please contact these third-party companies (e.g., Google) directly for more information about their privacy policy and your choices regarding the tags and the information collected by the tags.  \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"Auto\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eAutomated Information Collection\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eOur sites and mobile application(s) include social media features, such as the Facebook, Pinterest, and Twitter widgets. These features may collect information about you such as your IP address and which page you are visiting on our site. They may set a cookie or employ other tracking technologies to accomplish this. Social media features and widgets may be hosted by a third-party. Your interactions with those features are governed by the privacy policies of the companies that provide them.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"Social\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eSocial Media Widgets\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you use a mobile device, your device may share location information (when you enable location services) with our websites, mobile application(s), services or our service providers. For example, precise geo-location can be used to help you find nearby Target stores; or, in-store location through the use of your phone\u0026#8217;s blue tooth signal, LED light chip technologies or other technologies will permit Target to find nearby products for you, get you real-time deals, auto-sort your shopping list and more.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTo manage how you share your device\u0026#8217;s location settings, go to the \u003ca href=\\\"#Choices\\\"\u003e \u003ci\u003eChoices\u003c/i\u003e \u003c/a\u003e section of this privacy policy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"MLI\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eMobile Location Information\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe use cameras in and around our stores for operational purposes such as measuring traffic patterns and tracking in-stock levels. Cameras may also be used for fraud detection, theft prevention and security. When enabled, we may also use your device\u0026#8217;s camera (e.g., Apple\u0026#8217;s TrueDepth camera) so you can use services such as product visualization (e.g., see item in your space) or virtual try on services (e.g., try on accessories/beauty products). Information collected from your device\u0026#8217;s camera for these services is used in real time and is not stored on the servers. The virtual try on experience operates within your own device or browser and the data is deleted after the experience ends.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"StoreCam\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eCameras\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe collect information about you from other sources to enhance our existing Guest information and improve the accuracy of our records. This improves our ability to contact you and increases the relevance of our marketing.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca href=\\\"#\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold;\\\"\u003eBack to Top\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cdiv style=\\\"height: .45px; margin-top: 1rem; background-color: #333333;\\\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"InfoOther\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eInformation From Other Sources\u003c/span\u003e\"}],\"metadata\":{\"component_type\":\"Informative Text\",\"component_version\":\"02\"}},\"presentation\":\"/adaptive/c_web_a_0011/v02/mobile\"},\"1200\":{\"order\":1200,\"metadata\":{\"components\":[{\"title\":\"07.01.23_Global_Targetprivacypolicy_howinfoisused\",\"id\":\"WEB-379873\",\"type\":\"c_web_a_0011_v02\",\"type_name\":\"Informative Text\",\"content_type\":\"static\"}]},\"content\":{\"headline\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"InfoUsed\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cdiv style=\\\"text-align: left; color: #000000; font-size: 24px;\\\"\u003e3. How Is Your Information Used?\u003c/div\u003e\",\"info_text\":[{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eInformation we collect is used for a variety of purposes, including activities such as: processing transactions, helping our Guest Relations representatives resolve issues, identifying fraud and improving our services. In addition, information we collect improves your experience by delivering more personalized interactions and advertising in digital (e.g., Target.com, mobile app, other online sites) and social media (e.g., Facebook, Pinterest), as well as TV and Video platforms.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe also use information we collect for reporting and analysis purposes. We examine metrics such as how you are shopping on our website, in our stores and on our mobile application(s), the performance of our marketing efforts and your response to those marketing efforts.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eDeliver coupons, mobile offers newsletters, in-store receipt messages, emails, mobile messages, targeted advertising and social media notifications \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eProvide interactive features of the website or mobile application(s), such as product reviews or Weekly Ad, send marketing communications and other information regarding products, services and promotions\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eAdminister promotions, surveys, and focus groups\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eCross-context and cross-device linking\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eInterest-based advertising \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eImprove Guest experiences \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eConduct research and analysis\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003ePersonalize content, including using your image\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003ePerform other business activities as needed, or as described elsewhere in this policy\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"Purposes\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eOur Purposes (including but not limited to marketing)\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eFulfill and manage purchases, orders, payments, and returns/exchanges\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eRespond to requests for information about our products and services in our stores, on our websites or mobile application(s) or to otherwise serve you\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eConnect with you regarding Guest service via our contact center, Guest service desk, or on social media or internet chat platforms. Chat functionality allows our Guest Relations specialists to see what a Guest is typing before hitting the send button. This allows for quicker response time as our specialists anticipate questions. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eProvide services such as gift registry or a shopping list\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eAward and fulfill benefits associated with use of our services\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eAdminister sweepstakes and contests\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eConduct a transaction where we collect information required by law (for example, pseudoephedrine or age-restricted purchases) \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eAllow you to, using our mobile application(s): find a store nearest to your location, show you a map of the store (if available), use our drive up capabilities (where available), add and redeem offers, search for products and check availability, check prices, provide product ratings and reviews, track your orders, scan a UPC barcode or QR code, use voice recognition to add to your list, update information, etc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"Product\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eProduct and Service Fulfillment\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe merge data collected from our own websites and mobile application(s). Examples of the data collected include: cookie IDs, device advertising IDs, transaction and browsing history, your interaction with our online and mobile advertisements, including advertisements we serve within our emails and advertisements that we serve on behalf of third parties through Roundel, Target\u0026#8217;s in-house media company; information about ads we serve, such as which ad was served, your interactions with the ads, and the URLs where the ads are served by marketing partners such as Google.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eFor mobile platforms that require opt-in consent to link or track user or device data, unless you consent, Target does not link or track user or device data collected from Target application(s) with user or device data collected from other companies\u0026#8217; applications, websites or offline properties for targeted advertising or advertising measurement purposes. If a guest provides opt-in consent to the linking and use of data with a specifically identified third party partner, such data may be linked and may be used by Target and/or the third party partner as described at the time consent is obtained, including for targeted advertising or advertising measurement purposes. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"CC\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eCross-Context\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may also link your various devices so that content you see on one device can result in a relevant experience on another device. This allows us to deliver more personalized and consistent advertising to you. For example, if you purchase a product on our website using your desktop, we are able to avoid showing you an advertisement on the same product on your mobile phone; if you add an item to your cart on Target.com through your mobile device, but leave Target.com without purchasing the item, we are able to show you that item in your cart on another device.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"CDL\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eCross-Device Linking\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe participate in interest-based advertising (IBA), also known as online behavioral advertising (OBA). We use third-party advertising companies to display ads tailored to your individual interests based on how you browse and shop online, as well as to provide advertising-related services such as ad delivery, reporting, attribution, analytics, and market research. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe allow third-party companies to collect certain information when you visit our websites or use our mobile application(s). This information is used to serve ads for Target products or services or for the products or services of other companies when you visit this website or other websites. These companies use non-identifiable information (e.g., click stream information, browser type, time and date, subject of advertisements clicked or scrolled over, hardware/software information, and session ID) and personally identifiable information (e.g., static IP address) during your visits to this and other websites in order to provide advertisements about goods and services likely to be of greater interest to you. These parties typically use a cookie, web beacon or other similar tracking technologies to collect this information. Target adheres to the Digital Advertising Alliance (DAA) self-regulatory principles for IBA.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"IBA\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eInterest-Based Advertising\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIn order to improve Guest online and mobile shopping experiences, help with fraud identification, and assist our Guest Relations representatives in resolving issues Guests may experience in completing online purchases, we use tools to monitor certain user experience information; including login information, IP address, data regarding pages visited and ads clicked, specific actions taken on pages visited (e.g., information entered during checkout process), browser and device information.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"UserEx\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eUser Experience Information\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe engage with Guests on multiple social media platforms (e.g., Facebook, Twitter, and Pinterest). If you contact us on one of our social media platforms, request Guest service via social media, or otherwise direct us to communicate with you via social media, we may contact you via direct message or use other social media tools to interact with you. In these instances, your interactions with us are governed by this privacy policy as well as the privacy policy of the social media platform you use.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"SM\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eSocial Media\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may display targeted ads to you through social media platforms. These ads are sent to groups of people who share traits such as likely commercial interests and demographics. For example, we may target people who have expressed an interest in shopping for groceries, cosmetics, clothing, etc. See the policies of each social media platform for additional information about these types of ads.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"SMAds\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eSocial Media Ads\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003ePrevent fraudulent transactions, monitor against theft and otherwise protect our Guests and our business (e.g., product recalls)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"Prevent\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003ePrevention of Fraud and Other Harm\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eFor example, assist law enforcement and respond to legal/regulatory inquiries\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca href=\\\"#\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold;\\\"\u003eBack to Top\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cdiv style=\\\"height: .25px; margin-top: 1rem; background-color: #333333;\\\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca name=\\\"Legal\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eLegal Compliance\u003c/span\u003e\"}],\"metadata\":{\"component_type\":\"Informative Text\",\"component_version\":\"02\"}},\"presentation\":\"/adaptive/c_web_a_0011/v02/mobile\"},\"1300\":{\"order\":1300,\"metadata\":{\"components\":[{\"title\":\"07.01.23_Global_Targetprivacypolicy_howinfoisshared\",\"id\":\"WEB-379874\",\"type\":\"c_web_a_0011_v02\",\"type_name\":\"Informative Text\",\"content_type\":\"static\"}]},\"content\":{\"headline\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"InfoShared\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cdiv style=\\\"text-align: left; color: #000000; font-size: 24px;\\\"\u003e4. How Is Your Information Shared?\u003c/div\u003e\",\"info_text\":[{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may share the types and categories of personal information collected with the categories of third parties below.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe share the information we collect within Target Corporation, which includes all Target subsidiaries and affiliates. Target Corporation may use the information to offer you products and services that may be of interest to you. Target Corporation owns and operates Target stores, websites, mobile application(s), and issues the Target Debit Card. Target Corporation subsidiaries and affiliates include, but are not limited to Shipt, Inc.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"Subsid\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTarget Subsidiaries and Affiliates\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may share the information we collect with our banking partner, TD Bank USA N.A., which issues the Target MasterCard and Target Credit Card.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"CIB\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eCard Issuing Bank\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may share the information we collect with companies that provide support services to us (such as printers, email providers, mobile marketing services, analytics providers, web hosting providers, call center/chat providers, sweepstakes vendors, payment processors, coupon delivery vendors, data enhancement services, fraud prevention providers or shipping services providers, including product vendors) or that help us market our products and services. These companies may need information about you in order to perform their functions. We limit information shared with service providers to what is necessary to fulfill the services.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"ServPro\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eService Providers\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you create a gift registry or shopping list, your information will be accessible on our website, mobile or social application(s), on partner registries, and on kiosks in stores. If you purchase an item from a registry or shopping list, information such as your billing name and address will be made available to the list creator. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"RegShop\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eRegistries and Shopping Lists\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe allow other businesses to make their products or services available to our Guests (e.g. Target Plus Partners).  You may purchase products or services from these other businesses through our website or mobile application.  When you purchase such products or services, we will share personal information related to your purchase with those businesses.  Information received by those businesses in connection with a Target Plus purchase will be subject to the Target Plus Partner\u0026#8217;s privacy policy. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"OBP\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eOther Businesses Products and Services\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may disclose information we collect when we believe disclosure is appropriate to comply with the law; to enforce or apply applicable terms and conditions and other agreements; to facilitate the financing, securitization, insuring, sale, assignment, bankruptcy, or disposal of all or part of our business or assets; or to protect the rights property or safety of our company, our Guests or others.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"LegalReq\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eLegal Requirements\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eAt your direction or request, or when you otherwise consent, we may share your information.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"Else\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eElsewhere at Your Direction\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may share non-identifiable or aggregate information with third parties for lawful purposes.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"Sharing\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eSharing Non-identifiable or Aggregate Information with Third Parties\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIn connection with the sale or transfer of some or all of our business assets, we may transfer the corresponding information regarding our Guests. We also may retain a copy of that Guest information.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca href=\\\"#\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold;\\\"\u003eBack to Top\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cdiv style=\\\"height: .25px; margin-top: 1rem; background-color: #333333;\\\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"BT\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eBusiness Transfers\u003c/span\u003e\"}],\"metadata\":{\"component_type\":\"Informative Text\",\"component_version\":\"02\"}},\"presentation\":\"/adaptive/c_web_a_0011/v02/mobile\"},\"1400\":{\"order\":1400,\"metadata\":{\"components\":[{\"title\":\"07.01.23 Targetprivacypolicy_choices\",\"id\":\"WEB-379875\",\"type\":\"c_web_a_0011_v02\",\"type_name\":\"Informative Text\",\"content_type\":\"static\"}]},\"content\":{\"headline\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"Choices\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cdiv style=\\\"text-align: left; color: #000000; font-size: 24px;\\\"\u003e5. What Choices Do You Have?\u003c/div\u003e\",\"info_text\":[{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you do not wish to receive catalogs, coupons, and other promotional postal mail, call the privacy information line at \u003ca href=\\\"tel://1-800-831-6880\\\"\u003e1-800-831-6880\u003c/a\u003e to opt-out.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003ePostal Mail\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you do not wish to receive promotional telephone calls, call the privacy information line at \u003ca href=\\\"tel://1-800-831-6880\\\"\u003e1-800-831-6880\u003c/a\u003e to opt-out.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTelephone\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you do not wish to receive promotional emails from us, call the privacy information line at \u003ca href=\\\"tel://1-800-831-6880\\\"\u003e1-800-831-6880\u003c/a\u003e to opt-out. You also have the ability to unsubscribe from promotional emails via the unsubscribe link included in each promotional email. In some cases we may provide an unsubscribe link within an operational email (e.g., Guest surveys). \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eEmail\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eWe may send text messages you have consented to receive. You can cancel text messages at any time by texting \\\"STOP\\\". After you send \\\"STOP\\\", we may send you an additional text message to confirm that you have been unsubscribed. You will no longer receive text messages from that short code or number, as applicable, but you may receive text messages if you are subscribed to other text lists. If at any time you have questions about the text messages, text \\\"HELP\\\". After you send \\\"HELP\\\" we will respond with instructions on how to use our service as well as how to unsubscribe. Message and data rates may apply.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eText Messages\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eYou may opt-out from allowing Target to send you push notifications by adjusting the permissions in your mobile device. You may also choose which types of push notifications to receive by adjusting the permissions within your Target mobile application. This opt choice does not apply to in-app notifications.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003ePush Notifications\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eYou may prevent your mobile device from sharing your location data by adjusting the permissions on your mobile device or within the relevant app.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eGeo-Location and In-Store Location\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you no longer wish to be a Target Circle member, you can opt out of Target Circle \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.target.com/circle/optout\\\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you opt out of Target Circle, any accumulated Target Circle Earnings rewards and Community Giving Program votes will be deleted and you may not have access to other Target Circle benefits.  If you later re-join Target Circle, any deleted Target Circle Earnings rewards or Community Giving Program votes will not be reinstated.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTarget Circle\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eYou can stop all further collection of information by a Target mobile application by uninstalling the Target mobile application. You may use the standard uninstall process available as part of your mobile device or via the mobile application marketplace or network. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eNote: If you uninstall the mobile application from your device, the Target unique identifier associated with your device will continue to be stored. If you re-install the application on the same device, Target will be able to re-associate this identifier to your previous transactions and activities.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eUninstall a Target Mobile Application\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eThe help function of your browser should contain instructions on how to set your device to accept all cookies, to notify you when a cookie is issued or to not receive cookies at any time. If you set your device to not receive cookies at any time, certain personalized services cannot be provided to you, and accordingly, you may not be able to take full advantage of all of our features. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTo opt-out of the vendors we use for cross-device linking, go to the Digital Advertising Alliance\u0026#8217;s Choices page at www.aboutads.info/choices and perform a global opt-out on each browser and device that you would like to be opted out on. Opting out in this manner means that the browser on the device from which you opt-out will no longer receive information collected on devices linked to it, that devices linked to it will not receive information collected from the opted-out device, and that the vendor will not transfer information collected from the opted-out device to a third-party. Please note that this will not opt you out of cross-device linking or advertising across linked devices based solely on your visits to Target websites or application(s), or your interaction with advertisements for Target delivered by Target.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTo opt-out of our interest-based advertising for Target\u0026#8217;s goods and services or those of another party, online and in third-party mobile applications, visit Digital Advertising Alliance\u0026#8217;s Choices page \u003ca href=\\\"http://optout.aboutads.info\\\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e and perform a global opt-out. Options you select are browser and device specific.  \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTo learn more about interest-Based Advertising, visit the \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.networkadvertising.org/understanding-online-advertising\\\"\u003eNetwork Advertising Initiative website\u003c/a\u003e and the \u003ca href=\\\"http://www.aboutads.info/how-interest-based-ads-work\\\"\u003eDigital Advertising Alliance website\u003c/a\u003e. The opt-out tool described above is cookie-based.  Therefore, the opt-out will only function if your browser is set to accept third-party cookies, and it may not function where cookies are automatically disabled or removed. If you delete cookies, change your browser settings, switch browsers or computers, or use another operating system, you will need to opt-out again. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eCookies, Tracking, and Interest-Based Advertising\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eSome browsers have a \u0026#8220;do not track\u0026#8221; feature that lets you tell websites that you do not want to have your online activities tracked. At this time, we do not respond to browser \u0026#8220;do not track\u0026#8221; signals. However, Target treats Global Privacy Control signals as opt-out of sale and opt out of targeted/cross-context behavioral advertising requests under applicable state laws (e.g., California Consumer Privacy Act). \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eDo Not Track\u003c/span\u003e\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eAnalytics services such as Site Catalyst by Adobe Analytics, Google Analytics and Crazy Egg provide services that analyze information regarding visits to our websites and mobile application(s). They use cookies, web beacons, recorded interactions and other tracking mechanisms to collect this information. \u003c/span\u003e  \u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTo learn about Adobe Analytics privacy practices or to opt-out of cookies set to facilitate reporting, click \u003ca href=\\\"http://www.adobe.com/privacy.html\\\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTo learn more about Google\u0026#8217;s privacy practices, click \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/\\\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e. To access and use the Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on, click \u003ca href=\\\"https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout\\\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTo learn more about Crazy Egg\u0026#8217;s privacy practices, click \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.crazyegg.com/privacy\\\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e. To opt-out of Crazy Egg, click \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.crazyegg.com/opt-out\\\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e..\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003ca href=\\\"#\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold;\\\"\u003eBack to Top\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cdiv style=\\\"height: .25px; margin-top: 1rem; background-color: #333333;\\\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eOther Web Site Analytics Services\u003c/span\u003e\"}],\"metadata\":{\"component_type\":\"Informative Text\",\"component_version\":\"02\"}},\"presentation\":\"/adaptive/c_web_a_0011/v02/mobile\"},\"1500\":{\"order\":1500,\"metadata\":{\"components\":[{\"title\":\"07.01.23_TargetPrivacyPolicy_Loyalty/State-Specific\",\"id\":\"WEB-379876\",\"type\":\"c_web_a_0011_v02\",\"type_name\":\"Informative Text\",\"content_type\":\"static\"}]},\"content\":{\"headline\":\"\u003ca name=\\\"FIP\\\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cdiv style=\\\"text-align: left; color: #000000; font-size: 24px;\\\"\u003e6. Loyalty \u0026 Financial Incentive Program\\n\u003c/div\u003e\\n\",\"info_text\":[{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTarget Circle is a voluntary loyalty program.  By joining Target Circle, you receive: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e1% Earnings\u003c/b\u003e: You earn 1%* when you shop to redeem at Target later or continue saving 5%** with your RedCard. You cannot receive the RedCard 5% instant savings and earn the Target Circle 1% in the same transaction. \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHundreds of Deals\u003c/b\u003e: You get access to deals, plus offers just for you.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eBirthday Gift\u003c/b\u003e: You receive 5% off a shopping trip. Restrictions apply. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eCommunity Support\u003c/b\u003e: You help direct where Target gives in your community. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e*Terms and restrictions apply to the 1% reward. Program rules are available in store or at Target.com/RedCard\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTarget Circle members may have opportunities to redeem offers for products or services at select partners. otherwise consent, we may share your information with third parties (e.g., if a guest provides explicit, opt-in consent to the linking and use of data with a specifically identified third party partner, such data may be linked and may be used by Target and/or the third party partner as described at the time consent is obtained, including for targeted advertising or advertising measurement purposes).\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eNon-Discrimination\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eTarget will not discriminate against you because you exercise your rights.  For example, Target will not deny you goods or services or charge you a different price or rate for goods or services if you make an access, deletion, or do not sell request. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIf you are a California Resident, You Have the Following Rights Under the CCPA\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eRight to request Target disclose Personal Information, or categories of Personal Information, it collects, uses, discloses, and sells or shares for cross-context behavioral advertising\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eRight to request Target correct inaccurate personal information we maintain about you\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eRight to request Target delete Personal Information we have collected from you\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eRight to request Target opt you out of the sale of your Personal Information or sharing of your Personal Information for cross-context behavioral advertising.  Note: Target will also treat Global Privacy Control browser signals as opt-out of sale/sharing requests.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eProcess Used to Verify an Access, Correction, and/or Deletion Request\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you are a Target Guest, you will be required to submit information about yourself that Target will use to determine if we have information about you. If we are able to locate information about you, then we will fulfill your access, correction and/or deletion request. If we are not able to verify your information, then we may provide you with a report that includes the categories of personal information we collect, use, disclose, and sell or share.\u003cspan class=\\\"h-sr-only\\\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you have a Target.com account, your Access report will be placed in your account once it is ready.  You will need to sign into your account to view your report. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you do not have a Target.com account, you will receive two emails when your Access report is ready. These emails will be sent to the email address you provided at the time you submitted your request.  One email will contain a link to your report and a second email will contain a password needed to access the report.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eIf you are an authorized agent, then you will be required to submit your contact information as well as information about the Guest for whom you are making a request. As an authorized agent you will receive an email confirming that we have received the request along with a second email asking you to fill out a certification form confirming your information and certifying you have the right to make a request on behalf of the Guest. Once the report is ready, it will be sent to the email or physical address you have given us, depending on the delivery method you choose. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to Submit a Request\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eYou can submit a request using the methods listed below\u003c/span\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eAccess Requests: Contact the privacy information line at \u003ca href=\\\"tel://1-800-831-6880\\\"\u003e1-800-831-6880\u003c/a\u003e or click this \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.target.com/ccpa-intake-form\\\"\u003elink\u003c/a\u003e.  \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eCorrection Requests: Contact the privacy information line at \u003ca href=\\\"tel://1-800-831-6880\\\"\u003e1-800-831-6880\u003c/a\u003e or click this \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.target.com/guest-privacy/corrections\\\"\u003elink\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eDeletion Requests: Contact the privacy information line at \u003ca href=\\\"tel://1-800-831-6880\\\"\u003e1-800-831-6880\u003c/a\u003e or click this \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.target.com/ccpa-intake-form\\\"\u003elink\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eDo Not Sell or Share (for Cross-Context Behavioral Advertising) My Personal Information Requests: Click this \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.target.com/guest-privacy/\\\"\u003elink\u003c/a\u003e. Note: Target will also treat Global Privacy Control browser signals as opt-out of sale/sharing requests.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"subhead\":\"\"},{\"message\":\"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 120%\\\"\u003eBelow are metrics regarding Access, Delete and Do Not Sell My Personal Information requests submitted pursuant to the CCPA that Target received, fulfilled (in whole or in part), and denied between January 1, 2022 and December 31, 2022.
